		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />as blargg stated, the regulator makes quite a dent in power consumption.  If you could rather find a 5v battery (or combination of batteries making such voltage), you could bypass the regulator altogether.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


