		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Didn't the Game Boy and Game Boy Color use 5.0 V, from either four 1.5 V alkaline cells (GB) or two 1.5 V alkaline cells (GBC)? I wonder if we could steal such a regulator and power the NES that way.

		

